    "id": "2033596033331011668",
    "text": "John Oliver is still haunted by JD Vance’s debate with Tim Walz, warns Democrats are “in trouble” if they have to face him again.\n\nOLIVER: “Several times during that debate, Tim Walz actually said, ‘I agree with you.’ And once it was over, many analysts seemed surprised by what they’d just seen.”\n\nMEDIA: “Let’s face it, Vance looked very reasonable.”\n\n“He looked rational. He seemed at many moments to be reasonable.”\n\n“I was getting texts from Democrats, panicked, quite frankly, who were saying, ‘Wow, he’s really moderating himself on a lot of these issues. He’s the most likable he has ever been.’”\n\nOLIVER: “Yeah, it’s true… When the next election rolls around, if he can put that act back on when everyone is looking, we may be in trouble.”",
