    "text": "Tim Walz’ democracy answer was the best one of the night because it spoke to the real issue for vice presidential nominees— who is competent and what does the veep nominee say about the character of the their running mate. He drove home that Vance’s refusal to acknowledge the 2020 election’s legitimacy is a major red flag for Vance’s fitness.",
