    "text": "Hard to believe this veep debate moved the needle at all. Vance worked on raising his likability. Walz showed he knew his stuff but stumbled a few times. Vance lied about his support for an abortion ban, backed Trump's Big Lie &amp; refused to acknowledge the violence of 1/6. https://t.co/6oxvgEUVey",
